{"tid":2487981,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"柯歷利因想賣C朗而被炒","createTime":"2021-04-14T02:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T05:16:20.000Z","uid":31314,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb9612240cce44f472fe1c03c7757897aee9f67","tid":2487981,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:32:15.000Z","msg":"基斯坦奴朗拿度最近不時被批評只顧自己擦數據，不理會祖雲達斯的成績，原來前任主帥柯歷利早已曾要求球會放棄球王。基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）於2018年夏天以1億歐元從皇家馬德里改投祖雲達斯，跟時任教練柯歷利（Massimiliano Allegri）合作。<br />\n<br />\n意大利《共和報》爆料，<strong><span class=\"red\">柯歷利跟C朗合作了1季後，向會長艾尼利提議賣走這位葡萄牙球王，因為他阻礙了陣中年輕球員的上陣時間，減慢球隊的成長。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n不過，艾尼利不同意柯歷利，之後更辭退了對方，引入當時剛離開車路士的沙利。可是，沙利同樣未能帶領斑馬兵團取得成功，今季換了毫無執教經驗的派路。<br />\n<br />\n由於祖記今季戰績差勁，幾近確定未能成功衛冕，盛傳C朗將被賣走。意大利《米蘭體育報》指，<strong><span class=\"red\">C朗最近對於隊友表現不力十分不滿，包括中堅基亞連尼、翼鋒費達歷高基艾沙。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://en.as.com/en/imagenes/2019/05/19/football/1558246225_347523_noticia_normal.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.as.com%2Fen%2Fimagenes%2F2019%2F05%2F19%2Ffootball%2F1558246225_347523_noticia_normal.jpg&h=17d9ae8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39924ab769cd68f89124e59990dce5be73941709","tid":2487981,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"柯歷利<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753c0c8c72a8896705c1d4e47f78dd9feba9382f","tid":2487981,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"39924ab769cd68f89124e59990dce5be73941709","tid":2487981,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"柯歷利<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces